Locators

locating by number of element
  (//a)[1]
  (//div)[3]

 by text
  //span[contains(text(),'Photo')]
  //span[contains(text(),'googl')]

locating using part of the locator
useful for when elements change all the time

input[starts-with(@id='Aki_')]
input[contains(@id='Form_')]
- in the above case, Form_ is followed by a randomly generated string
- this will come in useful with the elements at MercuryGate


Multiple attributes

//a[@id=’id1’][@name=’namevalue1’]


